SEARCH
Package ru.introguzzle.parsers.xml.parse

Class Parser

java.lang.Object
ru.introguzzle.parsers.xml.parse.Parser
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, BaseParser<XMLDocument>
public abstract class Parser extends Object implements Serializable, BaseParser<XMLDocument>
Abstract base class for XML parsers. This class provides a common structure for parsers that utilize a Tokenizer to convert XML data into structured tokens. It also supports asynchronous parsing using an Executor.
